ignout/route.ts:10:      await supabase.auth.signOut();\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:1:# Market Research: Provodnik\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:5:`Provodnik` should enter the Russian tours and excursions market not as another generic listing site, but as a lower-commission marketplace focused on:\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:89:- Ключевые validated сигналы: 84% самоорганизуются, 63% через агрегаторы (Aviasales/Я.Путешествия/Островок/Tutu), only 3% через авторские туры; раннее бронирование рухнуло 16% → 8% за сезон; компании 3+ взрослых **+58% YoY**; Tripster использует ту же таксономию Индивидуальная / Групповая / Мини-группа, что валидирует Model 1/2/3 в каноне Provodnik.\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:94:## 5. Why Provodnik can exist\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:96:`Provodnik` has a viable reason to exist if it is built around a different market motion:\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:99:- `Provodnik` should be request-first plus listing support;\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:101:- `Provodnik` should monetize fragmented, custom, and budget-sensitive demand;\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:103:- `Provodnik` must match trust basics, then differentiate on liquidity for group and custom demand.\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:114:- `Provodnik`: lower-commission marketplace targeting `10% to 15%`.\n./docs/product/MARKET_RESEARCH.md:183:The research supports building `Provodnik`, but only under a clear strategic constraint:\n./docs/qa/finish-website-2026-06-28/sonnet-full-public-audit-task.md:22:- key detail pages if linked from cards and reachable without auth: sample `/requests/[id]`, `/listings/[id]`, `/guides/[slug]`, `/destinations/[slug]`.\n./audits/2026-05-12-ppfs-stage1/guide.md:3:Walk **partially deferred** — see auth blocker (P0) in `traveler.md`: the documented primary guide credential `dev+guide@rgx.ge` (and the demo `guide@provodnik.app` / `Demo1234!`, and the local-seed `Guide1234!`) **all reject on `provodnik.app` login** with «Неверный email или пароль.» No machine path to walk `/guide/*` routes systematically in this session.\n./audits/2026-05-12-ppfs-stage1/guide.md:7:2. Findings from the **signed-in** state of the very first navigation in this session (a stale browser cookie left a guide session active for one navigation before `/api/auth/signout` cleared it). One snapshot was captured before signout — surfaced below.\n./audits/2026-05-12-ppfs-stage1/guide.md:13:| /guide (Pre-Gate, with stale cookie) | PRE-GATE | 1. Land on `/` at session start with a pre-existing cookie from a prior tester. 2. Inspect nav. | Per LEGEND.md Pre-Guide-Route Gate: confirm `user_metadata.role` and `app_metadata.role` are both `guide` BEFORE visiting any `/guide/*` page. | Nav rendered the guide chrome — links to «Запросы / Календарь / Портфолио / Профиль / Личный кабинет / Сообщения / Выйти». Avatar \"D / Гид\". Did **not** inspect Supabase Application > Auth session for `role` before navigating away — the session was nuked by signout in step 2 to start the guest walk. | N/A | Re-walk required with the proper Pre-Gate dump (auth session JSON, role claims). | — |\n./audits/2026-05-12-ppfs-stage1/guide.md:14:| /guide (after signout) | UX | 1. Open `/guide` unauthenticated. | Redirect to `/auth`. | Redirects to `/auth` (confirmed via guest-side test of `/guide/dev-guide`). | N/A | — | — |\n./audits/2026-05-12-ppfs-stage1/guide.md:15:| /guides/[slug] (public profile, no auth) | UX | 1. Open `/guides/dev-guide` as guest. | Guide profile page. | Renders correctly **structurally**, but: (a) the bio paragraph is **mojibake** (`???????? ???.`), (b) the rating header reads `0.0 / 5 · 0 отзывов` and stat block `0.0 рейтинг / 0 поездок / 5 лет опыта` — zero-state UX implies a zero-star guide rather than a guide without reviews yet, (c) the «Готовые экскурсии» tiles re-use the listing-cards data and inherit the same mojibake-on-rows-1-and-2 issue seen on `/listings`. | N/A | (a) Encoding bug in seed bio